data.name: label16.Text
data.value: This app is meant to be used for formatting Zoom invite messages. You can create different templates (each for a different meeting) and use 6 different tags to automatically insert data into your templates: {link}, {id}, {pw}, {tel1}, {tel2} and {time}. If you need any help, please contact AvA.Soft. Thank you for using this app! :)

data.name: label12.Text
data.value: Meetings - you can set here your meetings' days and hours. They are used to automatically calculate the {time} tag when you use it in a template. The time is chosen from the next (or nearest) meeting from this list (based on the current settings).

data.name: chk_ImportKeepDup.ToolTip
data.value: How are duplicates checked? For templates - only the template name it's checked (since it has to be unique). The template data itself, is NOT checked. For meetings - the whole meeting is checked (description, day and time).
